%% Diagram: Grid library decision tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start[Need a data grid] --> Size{Dataset size?}
    Size -->|under 1K rows| Simple[Plain semantic table]
    Size -->|1K to 100K| Mid{Control requirements?}
    Size -->|over 100K| Large{Update frequency?}

    Mid -->|Full control| TanStack[TanStack Table plus react-virtual]
    Mid -->|Quick setup| MUI[MUI X DataGrid]
    Mid -->|Enterprise features| AG[AG Grid]

    Large -->|Static or paginated| ServerSide[Server-side row model]
    Large -->|Real-time updates| Canvas[Canvas-based or AG Grid Viewport]
